{
    "name": "Murderous Scythe",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Many of these murderers serve as assassins for dark druid circles or dominate savage humanoid tribes."
        },
        {
            "name": "Zelath the Reaper",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Knowing that death is just part of the cycle of life, Zelath truly believes his murderous ways enforces the will of nature. Like a deadly gardener, he prunes those who dare thwart death\u2019s call or despoil nature.<br/><br/><b>Combat Encounters</b>:Zelath aids other druids in the protection of their homes, bringing his unorthodox talents for mutual defense and strategic offense.<br/><br/><b>Roleplaying Suggestions</b>: Zelath often offers his expert knowledge of poisons to friends of the natural order."
        }
    ],
